Label: chalcone isomerase 3
Comment: Catalizes the conversion of cinnamoyl-CoA to pinocembrin chalcone

Label: (LOC_OS07G11440.1)
Comment:
a putative expresssed chalcone synthase which facilitates the conversion of 4-coumaroyl-CoA to isoliquiritigenin
Or the primary product of this enzyme could be 4,2',4',6'-tetrahydroxychalcone (also termed naringenin-chalcone or chalcone)
